# Tools and Utilities

Adventures require more than weapons and armor. The rope that lets you climb castle walls, the torch that illuminates dark dungeons, the grappling hook that bridges impossible gaps—these mundane tools solve problems that magic and muscle cannot.

While adventuring gear kits provide comprehensive loadouts for specific scenarios, tools and utilities represent individual items you choose based on your character's methods and the challenges you expect to face. Smart adventurers invest in the right tools before they're desperately needed.

